Instruction how to request for account deleting
For the Application “Show to me”
Developed by Berdnikov Artem

In order to request for deleting your account from the application send an email from your email address to the 1c.mk.ua@gmail.com with the text:
[email of you account] - delete

After your request for the account deleting all your data will be deleted from the application and it's databases including:
- your email
- your alias
- your orders
- your videos
- your locations
